dc_title_s: Political Boundary of Monterey County, California, 1994
dc_description_s: This shapefile is a gross-level polygon of the Monterey County political boundary intended for general mapping and planning purposes. The exact source of this layer is unknown, but believed to be from the California Coastal Commission WATER Project. This layer is part of a collection describing Geology resources and constraints Monterey County, California.The purpose of this data set is to delineate the Monterey County political boundary.
